他们在“一个旧驱动器上”发现了这段视频，他们认为该驱动器“已经永远消失了”。</p><p>专辑中的其他歌曲包括：《Money to Burn》（后来收录在他们 2005 年演示专辑《Climbing to New Lows》中）、《Funky Legal Beats》和《I Am One of the Smartest Apes in the World》。</p><p>在这里查看视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="MGMT -“Funky Legal Beats”2003 年 4 月 20 日音乐会第二部分" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zDgknnsguZQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="MGMT - “Money to Burn”2003 年 4 月 20 日音乐会第 3 部分" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zN4C9eNSRrQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="MGMT - “This Must be the Place”高清原创 4/20/03 音乐会第 4 部分" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/U3InTIqCMYo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="MGMT - “Kids” 原版 2003 年 4 月 20 日音乐会第 5 部分" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vNC1W2m4Uug?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> MGMT <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/mgmt-loss-of-life-tiktok-streaming-3591861">在二月份接受了<em>NME</em>采访，</a>谈论了他们于 2 月 23 日发行的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mgmt-loss-of-life-review-lyrics-tracklist-3591340">《Loss O