伦敦夜总会 Heaven 执照吊销后将于明天重新开业https://www.nme.com/news/music/london-nightclub-heaven-will-re-open-tomorrow-after-license-suspension-3819865?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=london-nightclub-heaven-will-许可证暂停后明天重新开放Emma WilkesFri, 06 Dec 2024 18:40:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3819865 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦查令十字区的天堂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据称，一名妇女在“会场附近”被天堂保安人员强奸，该场馆被警方关闭。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/london-nightclub-heaven-will-re-open-tomorrow-after-license-suspension-3819865">伦敦夜总会 Heaven 将于明天重新开业，此前</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先出现了执照吊销的消息。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦查令十字街的天堂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/london-heaven-rob-pinney-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦夜店 Heaven 上个月被警方关闭后，已获准明天（12 月 7 日）重新开业。</p><p>位于伦敦市中心查令十字路口的著名LGBTQIA+场所， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heaven-nightclub-shut-down-after-member-of-staff-arrested-and-charged-with-rape-3813258">11月15日以公共安全为由，被威斯敏斯特警方吊销酒类经营许可证28天</a>。</p><p>此举是在一名妇女据称于 11 月 1 日“在会场附近”被天堂保安人员强奸后采取的。警方声明继续称，其他工作人员随后“据称忽视了她报告袭击事件的努力”。</p><p>一名安全人员随后被捕并被指控犯有强奸罪，目前正在监狱还押。</p><p>当时，威斯敏斯特警方指出，五月份发生了一次事件，当时俱乐部安全团队的三名成员被拍摄在街上袭击顾客。</p><p>警方声明总结说：“这些事件引起了对场地履行其保护客户义务的能力的严重关注，尤其是在保护客户方面。”</p><p>在有关今天（12月6日）暂停许可证暂停的听证会之后，威斯敏斯特许可小组委员会已允许天堂重新开放。根据<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/gay-club-heaven-rape-closure-westminster-city-council-licence-b1198525.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>标准</em></a>，已经实施了几个新条件，包括凌晨3点的最后一个条件，禁止排队饮酒和修改安全性。这些新措施旨在保护“弱势”客户是俱乐部队列中“机会主义罪犯”的目标。</p><p>该场地在Instagram上写道：“有很多人要感谢，但是我需要花几天的时间才能将自己的想法融合在一起，因为最近几周在精神和身体上都在耗尽。”</p><p> “但是今天，一个普遍的感谢。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDPsfRlCGtu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; hei